{
  "texts": [
    "We determined there was sufficient support for some of the themes, for example, the discussion of the rise of formal rules and laws around smoking is prevalent in some of the books even though we had not noticed it previously.",
    "However, we determined other themes to be more marginal and out of sync with their prominent place in ChatGPT's analysis.",
    "For example, technological developments like vaping are discussed in only 1 of the 21 documents and are not a prevalent theme even in that text.",
    "As a result, even though technological changes were relevant in one of the books and could be seen as a source of variation for the very reason that they were not discussed consistently, we determined there was insufficient evidence for the inclusion of technology as a major theme or source of change in smoking norms.",
    "We then repeated the analytical query with different hyperparameters, and we examined any new results, adding any that we determined to be sufficiently robust to the list of major themes and sources of change."
  ]
